{"tid":1760672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 以後記得唔好叫建制派","createTime":"2019-11-28T11:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T20:36:54.000Z","uid":210755,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b00bed74b7fc516d76a55a721346989527f929","tid":1760672,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"真係真係要記住, 唔好再叫民建聯同工聯會 做建制派<br />\n最好叫 親共派 / 親共反對派<br />\n (專反民意,與民為敵) <br />\n哩d親共大黨做中共白手套做到出哂面,你地仲叫佢做建制派 幫佢地做文宣, <br />\n仲有起碼數以百萬人 將建制派同穩定掛勾, 咁多年嘅洗腦觀念<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為無用, 唔好低估港豬嘅數量 一人一啖口水都浸死你.<br />\n我地要灌輸嘅觀係, 諗起民建聯 工聯會, 就係親共, 就諗起極權反民意 與民為敵<br />\n<br />\n一年,兩年 可能有幾千人再轉軚, <br />\n4年5年, 十年,十五年,二十年, 形成根深蒂固嘅本土意識,香港核心價值,去團結 吸納數十萬 甚至百萬 游離派/港豬/離地L<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39617b99507c37d9aa47331ba52a4edaa351dbf","tid":1760672,"uid":234679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"非民主派"},{"pid":"f29739f6645bc2c72c1f62ef4705d08de673a294","tid":1760672,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"無錯 唔好比支那同埋cctvb同化<br />\n成撚日用埋啲蝗語<br />\n當年泡菜去中國化真係好有遠見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787d7d9aec688afc15beb4ff494a95ecd5785832","tid":1760672,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"奶共<br />\n共狗<br />\n賣港派<br />\n港奸<br />\n港共走狗"},{"pid":"247e2c3a44bb826d9ee9507c8bd575512966d8b1","tid":1760672,"uid":104833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"少數保皇派"},{"pid":"2bd457c1530591fe10a54cc0e0c45f8a082a4ebd","tid":1760672,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T18:40:04.000Z","ms